                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Tash and Malo are your friend here.<br /><br />Me, Ench buddy, and Shm have trio'd the first floor.  Of course just the regular mobs and not maestro.<br /><br /><br />Here is what we did.  Zoned in, shm makes pet, Ench makes pet.  I do not make pet.  Grab the first undead that I can (being very careful not to get a buttload of mobs) .  Usually start with 4 mobs aggroed.  Chanter mezzes all. Chanter and Shm tash and malo them all.  Chanter gets rid of pet.  Me and chanter now charm the two we like the best.  (I find Clerics of Innoruk to be the best).  Augment the sucker (Keep ST memmed)  Use those 2 pets plus the shaman for spot heals and extra dmg and you'll clean house.<br /><br />Just takes some coordination.  Usually at 6 minutes or so we get a stopping point and chanter will remez my mob (after I feign), so I can recharm.<br /><br />I then do the same for his.<br /><br />Works well.  And very exciting when you get a few mobs around ya<br /><br />Craigmandu<br />56th Defiler<br />On Tarrew Marr</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
